CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 12, 1959, pg. A3 reads: "Having Fun - Mothers, their youngsters and visitors turned out in large numbers, last Friday night, to enjoy the "Back-to-School Festival," which consisted of games, contests, a dance and outdoor movies. This group is from Whiteside Rd. - Harris Photos."Printed image flipped by Pittsburgh Courier
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women and children gathered for "Back To School" Festival outside an apartment building, Whiteside Road
